ides contract manufacturing services. The company offers its products under Tedibar, Shelcal, Unienzyme, and Ahaglow brands. The company was formerly known as Trinity Laboratories and changed its name to Torrent Pharmaceuticals Limited in 1971. The company was founded in 1959 and is based in Ahmedabad, India. Torrent Pharmaceuticals Limited is a subsidiary of Torrent Investments Limited."}}